author: Paul Cullen, Olivia Kelly, Gerry Moriarty
title: Coronavirus: 16 more people have died in Republic as public urged to ‘have patience’
description: Over 700,000 people receiving unemployment payments from State
content:
The deaths of another 16 patients - 10 males and six females - diagnosed with Covid-19 have been reported on Monday by the National Public Health Emergency Team.
